      </p>
      <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:800;font-size:var(--text-3xl);margin-bottom:clamp(40px,6vw,60px);color:var(--text);">
        <span class="inline-en">Experience &amp; <span class="gradient-text">Education</span></span>
        <span class="inline-bn" style="font-family:var(--font-bn)">অভিজ্ঞতা ও <span class="gradient-text">শিক্ষা</span></span>
      </h2>
      <div style="position:relative;">
        <!-- Timeline vertical line -->
        <div style="position:absolute;left:8px;top:0;bottom:0;width:1px;background:linear-gradient(180deg,var(--accent),rgba(180,255,87,0.1));"></div>
        {timeline.map((item, i) => (
          <div
            class="reveal"
            style={`
              display:flex;gap:24px;margin-bottom:40px;padding-left:8px;
              animation:${item.side === 'right' ? 'slideInRight' : 'slideInLeft'} 0.6s var(--ease-expo) ${i*0.1}s both;
            `}
          >
            <div style="
              width:16px;height:16px;border-radius:50%;
